{"type":"message","id":"72038e42","parentId":"7fcd22ff","timestamp":"2026-04-05T02:31:11.926Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_WxpsfB9IthZo7oZEmxnsRo31|fc_05bdd3a20628929c0169d1c96d476c8191828c9e5732808f2d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MISSION.md\n\nLer o dispatch payload no disco, validar que compiled_entities_path existe, executar target building via helper Python, e validar que os artifacts de output (intake + report) existem no disco. Resultado baseado em artifacts no disco, nao em output conversacional.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775356271905}}
{"type":"message","id":"51713252","parentId":"72038e42","timestamp":"2026-04-05T02:31:11.945Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_xEh8kvt3fpsUUTNtuZufyZzr|fc_05bdd3a20628929c0169d1c96d4778819182931d559f07c206","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# CONTRACT.md\n\n## Input\nDispatch message com:\n- `compiled_entities_path` — path para compiled_entities.json do S3\n- `sector_root` — path raiz do sector S4\n- `job_id`\n- `video_id`\n- `account_id`\n- `language`\n\n## Output minimo\n- `<sector_root>/intake/research_intake.json` (contract_version: s4.research_intake.v1)\n- `<sector_root>/intake/target_builder_report.md`\n\n## Path handling\nUsar paths exactamente como recebidos. Nunca reconstruir.\n\n## Success\nAmbos os ficheiros existem no disco e research_intake.json e non-empty.\n\n## Failure\nExplicita, com razao. Nunca sucesso ambiguo.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775356271926}}
{"type":"message","id":"e38c1e98","parentId":"51713252","timestamp":"2026-04-05T02:31:11.971Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_pgudo9Mna74yJ6j6N4yi7zZW|fc_05bdd3a20628929c0169d1c96d477c8191b13307ef2ce75b54","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# OPERATIONS.md\n\n## Sequencia\n\n1. Parse activation message para: compiled_entities_path, sector_root, job_id, video_id, account_id, language.\n2. Validar que compiled_entities_path existe no disco.\n3. Executar helper:\n   `exec python \"C:\\Users\\User-OEM\\Desktop\\OpenClaw Workspace\\content_factory_block2\\S4\\helpers\\target_builder.py\" <compiled_entities_path> <sector_root> <job_id> <video_id> <account_id> <language>`\n4. Validar que intake existe: `<sector_root>/intake/research_intake.json`\n5. Validar que report existe: `<sector_root>/intake/target_builder_report.md`\n6. Reportar resultado baseado em artifacts no disco.\n\n## Regras\n\n- Estado no disco > conversa.\n- Falha explicita > sucesso ambiguo.\n- Nao inventar outputs inexistentes.\n- Nao considerar concluido apenas por resposta textual.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1775356271926}}
